OL,3,CFormer postal clerk: 'I considered
OL,4,Ctaking my own life' after wrongly
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FFormer postal clerk Joanne Cropper has
OL,8,Fbeen speaking to Granada Reports
OL,9,FCorrespondent Mel Barham
OL,11,FA former postal clerk says she is
OL,12,Fstill waiting for an apology - on the
OL,13,Fday a damning report is released into
OL,14,Fthe Post Office Horizon IT scandal.
OL,16,FJoanne Cropper was a clerk at a post
OL,17,Foffice in Winton in Ashton-under-Lyne,
OL,18,Fin Greater Manchester, but she was
OL,19,Fsacked and prosecuted after an error
OL,20,Fshowed the accounts were missing
OL,21,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
