OL,3,CFormer postal clerk: 'I considered
OL,4,Ctaking my own life' after wrongly
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FShe was fined and forced to pay back
OL,8,Fthe money lost, to the tune of more
OL,9,Fthan #4,000.
OL,11,FBut it was the emotional toll it took
OL,12,Fon her and her family that she said
OL,13,Fmade her nearly take her own life.
OL,15,FThe report, issued as part of the long-
OL,16,Frunning inquiry into the faulty
OL,17,FHorizon IT system concluded that at
OL,18,Fleast 13 people may have taken their
OL,19,Fown lives after being accused of
OL,20,Fwrongdoing
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
