OL,3,CFormer postal clerk: 'I considered
OL,4,Ctaking my own life' after wrongly
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FJoanne says she could have been part
OL,8,Fof that statistic: "It wasn't just the
OL,9,Fimpact on my me, it was the impact on
OL,10,Fmy whole family.
OL,12,F"I contemplated taking my own life
OL,13,Fbecause that way they would be left
OL,14,Falone, but how do you tell your
OL,15,Fdaughter and your family you are doing
OL,16,Fit to keep them happy to get them away
OL,17,Ffrom it all."
OL,19,FJoanne says that her life was made
OL,20,Falmost unbearable as she was punished
OL,21,Ffor a crime she did not commit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
