OL,3,CFormer postal clerk: 'I considered
OL,4,Ctaking my own life' after wrongly
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,F"I watched my family being bullied,"
OL,8,Fshe said. "People looking at me and
OL,9,Fsaying things that weren't true.
OL,11,F"I was basically scared of going out
OL,12,Finto my own village because of the
OL,13,Fnastiness of people who I'd grown up
OL,14,Fwith."
OL,16,FThe report described the impact on
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters as "disastrous" and
OL,18,Fsaid it heard evidence from 59 others
OL,19,Fwho had also contemplated suicide as a
OL,20,Fresult of the pressures from the
OL,21,Fscandal.
