OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FThe inquiry estimates that as many as
OL,8,F10,000 people may have been affected
OL,9,Fby the Horizon scandal, including both
OL,10,Fconvicted subpostmasters and those who
OL,11,Fexperienced financial or reputational
OL,12,Fdamage as a result of the system's
OL,13,Ffailures.
OL,15,FJoanne had her conviction quashed and
OL,16,Fsaid: "I was more excited about that
OL,17,Fthen the redress because the
OL,18,Fheadquarters decided it wasn't me".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
